{"tid":2457002,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"狂賀！[假] 古著Vintaholic 終於收皮！！！","createTime":"2021-03-22T10:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T05:48:54.000Z","uid":56076,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7512c489719aeb29f3de312e0d49b93830c538","tid":2457002,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"支01唔貼link<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關本月首次破獲涉及懷疑冒牌古著案，分別在落馬洲管制站、旺角古着零售店及荃灣倉庫，檢獲約9,300件懷疑冒牌古着及40個懷疑冒牌手袋，估計市值約530萬元，並拘捕古著店的男東主及一名女售貨員，被捕人士正保釋候查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtaQ9gm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtaQ9gm.png&h=fd6519ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關版權及商標跨境調查組指揮官司徒志輝表示，本12日在落馬洲管制站，人員經風險管理揀選一輛貨車進行檢驗，在兩個來自泰國及阿拉伯聯合酋長國空運快遞中，檢獲75件懷疑冒牌古著及40個懷疑冒牌手袋，市值約6萬元。海關經深入調查及商標持有人的協助下，本月16日採取執法行動，突擊搜查一間古著店位的旺角零售點及荃灣倉庫，檢獲約9,200件古著，市值約526萬元，並拘捕兩名23歲男東主及22歲女售貨員，他們正保釋候查。<br />\n<br />\n司徒志輝稱，近年市民對個人化衣着漸趨喜愛，特別喜好20、30年前出產的款式，坊間稱為古著，海關不排除有人為增加利潤魚目混珠，將真假古著混在一起出售。涉案古著店經營1年半，主要在亞洲地區包括泰國、巴基斯坦、韓國及日本進口古着，當中包括冒牌貨，送到貨倉後經篩選、翻新及清洗工序，再售賣予本地顧客，衛衣售價介乎500至700元，外套則1500至3500元，是類近款式三至八成價錢。"},{"pid":"208034bcd0649284d0d2971dca0bb6e57269605d","tid":2457002,"uid":56076,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"仲話出律師信喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af9b5deeac9b4cc40ff04b3daeef00fd970451f","tid":2457002,"uid":130079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拜托順便查下黃世澤條戇鳩d口罩係咪食落肚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高質簽名檔<br />\n================================<br />\n[評論黃世澤幾分鐘] 比較一下乳酪蛋糕食譜同黃世澤評論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2447077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2447077</a><br />\n[評論黃世澤幾分鐘] 分析下沈旭暉同黃世澤既分別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gKzkmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gKzkmS</a><br />\n[戇鳩警報器: 黃世澤 | martin oei | 交加街38號 ] 警世 黃世澤係令大家用唔到BNO移民既始作俑者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gHfHES\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gHfHES</a><br />\n[世澤日記] 細良一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2449877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2449877</a>"},{"pid":"e9b6236e971500ac85ec559c13af778133ddbc8b","tid":2457002,"uid":56076,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"之前有巴絲出完追擊post，都繼續有咁多傻豬幫襯真係谷鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家人都拉埋啦各位傻豬睇清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02df3ddb8baa512e2dc3b51e2fdc33f5e425fb50","tid":2457002,"uid":56076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"見佢成日又執又開都覺得奇怪啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8ed705d0dc12c28f095118765df7d88b28aaf4","tid":2457002,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a841173bcb9af93f1192431c66afa3e87a0624e","tid":2457002,"uid":20302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"終於<img